# Integration tests for Del Mercado API
# To run these tests, install the "REST Client" extension in VS Code.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### 1. Test Server Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Accept: application/json

### 2. Trigger Bulk Create load for Users
POST {{baseUrl}}/usuarios/bulk
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Trigger Bulk Create load for Products
POST {{baseUrl}}/produtos/bulk
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. CRUD - Get All Products
GET {{baseUrl}}/produtos
Accept: application/json

### 5. CRUD - Create a New Product (Manual)
POST {{baseUrl}}/produtos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Nome": "Teclado Mecânico Del Company RGB",
  "Descrição": "Teclado mecânico gamer switch blue premium com iluminação RGB",
  "Categoria": "eletronicos",
  "Preço": 249.99,
  "Percentual de desconto": 10.0,
  "Quantidade": 15,
  "Marca": "Del Company",
  "Imagem": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1618384887929-16ec33fab9ef"
}

### 6. CRUD - Get Product by ID (assuming ID 1 exists)
GET {{baseUrl}}/produtos/1
Accept: application/json

### 7. CRUD - Update Product (assuming ID 1 exists)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/produtos/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Nome": "Produto Teste Modificado",
  "Preço": 99.99,
  "Quantidade": 20
}

### 8. CRUD - Get All Users
GET {{baseUrl}}/usuarios
Accept: application/json

### 9. CRUD - Create a New User (Manual)
POST {{baseUrl}}/usuarios
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Nome": "Eliel",
  "Sobrenome": "Bernardi",
  "Idade": 21,
  "E-mail": "eliel.teste@gmail.com",
  "Telefone": "48991004282",
  "Endereço": "Rua Bathuel de Oliveira, 189",
  "Cidade": "Tijucas",
  "Estado": "SC"
}

### 10. CRUD - Update User (assuming ID 1 exists)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/usuarios/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Nome": "Nome Modificado",
  "Idade": 22
}

### 11. Transaction - Successful Movement: SAIDA (Decrease Stock)
# Deducts stock, calculates discount and final price
POST {{baseUrl}}/compras
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "codUsuario": 1,
  "codProduto": 1,
  "tipoMovimento": "SAIDA",
  "quantidadeMovimentada": 2,
  "formaPagamento": "CREDITO",
  "statusCompra": "PAGA"
}

### 12. Transaction - Successful Movement: ENTRADA (Increase Stock)
# Increases stock
POST {{baseUrl}}/compras
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "codUsuario": 1,
  "codProduto": 1,
  "tipoMovimento": "ENTRADA",
  "quantidadeMovimentada": 10,
  "formaPagamento": "DEBITO",
  "statusCompra": "PAGA"
}

### 13. Transaction - Failed Movement (Out of stock error validation)
# Should return HTTP 400 Bad Request with "Saldo insuficiente em estoque"
POST {{baseUrl}}/compras
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "codUsuario": 1,
  "codProduto": 1,
  "tipoMovimento": "SAIDA",
  "quantidadeMovimentada": 9999,
  "formaPagamento": "DINHEIRO",
  "statusCompra": "PENDENTE"
}

### 14. Report - Get All Transaction Movement Logs
GET {{baseUrl}}/compras
Accept: application/json

### 15. View Report - Critical Products (estoque < 10)
GET {{baseUrl}}/compras/relatorios/produtos-criticos
Accept: application/json

### 16. View Report - Financial Volume bought per Product
GET {{baseUrl}}/compras/relatorios/volume-compras
Accept: application/json

### 17. Chart Data - Physical Stock and Top 5 Financial Sales
GET {{baseUrl}}/compras/relatorios/graficos
Accept: application/json
